cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use HELIX in your research, please cite it using the metadata below."
type: software
title: "HELIX: Hierarchical Execution and Lifecycle Intelligence eXecutor"
abstract: "Self-healing middleware for ROS 2 robotic systems. Detects node failures,
  sensor anomalies, and log-pattern faults autonomously, then recovers through a
  three-tier escalation ladder — rule-based, adaptive, and on-device LLM-assisted
  diagnosis — without human intervention. Built for the Unitree GO2 quadruped on
  ROS 2 Humble with Jetson Orin."
